ckly Find New Blocks</b></h3><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Perhaps one of the best features of WordPress‚Äôs new and improved block editor is that you can quickly search for the blocks you might need for your content with the new block directory feature.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Simply search for any block that you might need, and the block directory will pull up the best matching results for you based on WordPress‚Äôs list of</span><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/browse/block/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b> plugins categorized as blocks</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3000d46 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"3000d46\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58080d6 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"58080d6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e23cbb1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e23cbb1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"935\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"WordPress 5.5 Next Release\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2.png 1920w, htt