//wpdeveloper.net/?p=480915\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:546:\"<p>EmbedPress will let embed anything and everything just with a click from more than 75+ sources link just with a click. You just have to get the link, insert and it will automatically fetch and display the content just the way it belongs to. This also works in the same way for Google Form.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/embed-google-forms-in-wordpress/\">How to Embed Google Forms In WordPress &amp; Collect User Data</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net\">WPDeveloper</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Afrin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8421:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Have you ever felt the necessity to </span><a href=\"https://embedpress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><b>embed Google Forms</b></a>¬†in your WordPress for running<span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> online surveys or collecting user data?</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> If you tried and thought it\'s difficult to do so, then we have good news for you! Using <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/embedpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">EmbedPress</a>, you can embed Google Forms in seconds, without any coding or extra hassle. Sounds awesome, right? Let‚Äôs explore in detail.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"more-480915\"></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Google-Forms-in-WordPress-Collect-User-Data.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-480985\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Google-Forms-in-WordPress-Collect-User-Data.png\" alt=\"embed Google Forms in WordPress\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Google-Forms-in-WordPress-Collect-User-Data.png 1280w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Google-Forms-in-WordPress-Collect-User-Data-600x338.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Google-Forms-in-WordPress-Collect-User-Data-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Introducing </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">EmbedPress &#8211; your <a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/embedpress-embed-anything-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ultimate embedding solution</a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> to embed anything in WordPress from more than 75+ sources. You don‚Äôt have to bother for adding any code or doing any manual work, you just have to insert the link and get your audience‚Äôs attention instantly with interactive content. The best part is you can use this plugin </span><b>absolutely with your favorite editors &#8211; Gutenberg, Classic Editor and <a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/go/elementor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Elementor Page Builder</a></b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.¬†</span></p>\n<h2><b>Why Should You Embed Google Forms?</b></h2>\n<p>If you are thinking about collecting user information, planning for any surveys, questionnaires, any administrative forms, security validation forms<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, or more, <strong><a href=\"https://embedpress.com/docs/embed-google-forms-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Google Forms</a></strong> is the easiest way that you can keep track of. You don‚Äôt have to roam around anywhere, just with a few clicks you can set up any kind of forms without any hassle. Also, you don‚Äôt have to worry about saving it or to do any storage.¬†</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">That‚Äôs why the business owner or individuals feel the </span><b>necessity of embedding Google Forms </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">on their website. So that they easily run and track their survey, collects user data or more without taking any other 3rd party support.¬†</span></p>\n<p><em><strong>Note: You need to¬†install and activate <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/embedpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">EmbedPress Plugin</a> to embed Google Forms in a WordPress site.</strong></em></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If you have successfully installed the plugin, then you are ready to embed anything on your desired WordPress editors along with Google Forms.</span></p>\n<h2><b>How To Embed Google Forms In WordPress Using EmbedPress</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If you want to embed Google Forms in WordPress, you just have to follow some simple </span><a href=\"https://embedpress.com/docs/embed-google-forms-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><b>step by step guideline</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> below:¬†</span></p>\n<h3><b>Embed Google Forms Instantly In </b><b>Gutenberg Editor</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You just have to copy the link of your </span>Google Forms and insert it on the Gutenberg editor and hit the<b> &#8216;Embed\' </b>button<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. That‚Äôs it! It will automatically fetch and display your feed outstandingly without any coding.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/loyDNFkkMT.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-481018 size-full\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/loyDNFkkMT.gif\" alt=\"Embed Google Forms In WordPress\" width=\"1341\" height=\"503\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><b>Embed Google Forms In WordPress Classic Editor¬†</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Similarly for </span><b>Classic Editor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, you have to get the exact link of your Google Forms that you want to embed and insert it on the editorial panel. It will then automatically fetch and embed Google Forms in WordPress site just with a click.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/R2XFlkQ77B.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-481019 size-full\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/R2XFlkQ77B.gif\" alt=\"Embed Google Forms In WordPress \" width=\"1048\" height=\"622\" /></a></p>\n<h3><b>Embed Google Forms In</b><b>¬†Elementor</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To start embedding your desired </span><b>Google Forms in most popular page builder Elementor, </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">you have to follow some steps that are mentioned below:</span></p>\n<h4><b>Step 1: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You have to find out the EmbedPress widget from the Elementor </span><b>&#8216;Search\' </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">panel. Then,</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">¬†drag & drop EmbedPress element on the desired section.</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1591887953519-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-481021\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1591887953519-1.png\" alt=\"Embed Google Forms In WordPress \" width=\"1348\" height=\"451\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1591887953519-1.png 1348w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1591887953519-1-600x201.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/screely-1591887953519-1-768x257.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1348px) 100vw, 1348px\" /></a></span></h4>\n<h4><b>Step 2: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> You just have to copy and paste the link of your desire forms data on the </span><b>&#8216;Embedded Link\'</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> panel. Then it will automatically track and publish your content just the way it is.</span></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/merge_from_ofoct.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-482603\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/merge_from_ofoct.gif\" alt=\"Embed Google Forms In WordPress\" width=\"1328\" height=\"580\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">EmbedPress made it easiest than ever before to <strong>embed Google Forms</strong> in WordPress.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> You don‚Äôt have to bother with coding, nor to give any extra effort to embed anything include Google Forms. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Haven‚Äôt try </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/plugins/embedpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><b>EmbedPress</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> yet? Let‚Äôs explore it‚Äôs amazing embedding functionalities and share your opinion by commenting below.¬†</span></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"How To Embed Google Forms In WordPress\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2ZZAvZmZ9yg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/embed-google-forms-in-wordpress/\">How to Embed Google Forms In WordPress &amp; Collect User Data</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net\">WPDeveloper</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http: